title: Missing crew members found dead after fighter jet crash in Washington state
description: Two US Navy aviators were found dead after their EA-18G Growler jet crashed near Mount Rainier during a training flight. Search teams, including a Navy helicopter and Army Special Forces, located the wreckage in a remote, densely wooded area. The Navy has transitioned to a salvage operation and is investigating the cause of the crash.
